(1, 'The Historic Hutchinson Fox Theatre', '', '<p><strong>2020 - 2021 Live Season</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"auto\" src=\"images/90thLogo.jpg\" width=\"100%\" /></strong></p>\r\n', '<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"auto\" src=\"images/2020-2021_Sponsos.jpeg\" width=\"100%\" /></p>\r\n', 'images/sponsors_home.jpeg', '<p><strong>THE FOX FILM SERIES IS BACK!</strong><br />\r\n<strong>NOW PLAYING</strong><br />\r\n<strong>NOMADLAND</strong><br />\r\nStarring Frances McDormand<br />\r\n<strong><a href=\"https://www.searchlightpictures.com/nomadland/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\">Official Site</span></a></strong><br />\r\nFollowing the economic collapse of a company town in rural Nevada, Fern (Frances McDormand) packs her van and sets off on the road exploring a life outside of conventional society as a modern-day nomad. The third feature film from director Chlo&eacute; Zhao, NOMADLAND features real nomads Linda May, Swankie and Bob Wells as Fern&#39;s mentors and comrades in her exploration through the vast landscape of the American West.<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" height=\"444\" src=\"images/Nomadland.jpg\" width=\"300\" /><br />\r\n<strong>Friday, March 26th, 7:30 PM<br />\r\nSaturday, March 27th, 7:30 PM<br />\r\nSunday, March 28th, 2:00 PM</strong><br />\r\n2021, R, 107 Minutes<br />\r\nAdmission only $5 per person, per movie. Doors open 45 minutes prior to showtime. Film Series passes include 10 Admissions and a punch card for five FREE small popcorns for only $45, good for any Fox Film Series movie. Passes available at the door.<br />\r\nWe are excited to announce the addition of classic cartoons presented prior to each Fox Film Series movie! Enjoy selections from Betty Boop, Popeye, Little Audrey, Casper, and many more while you settle in for the feature presentation!<br />\r\nMore Fox Film Series information <a href=\"films.php\">HERE</a></p>\r\n', 'Announcements', 'images/fox_oldstyle.jpg', 0);

