tyle=\"font-size:smaller\"><em>(<u>Membership is tax-deductible less value of tickets</u>)</em></span><br />\r\n1) Concert level benefits<br />\r\n2) One card for five free popcorns<br />\r\n3) Four tickets to a Fox Live Season show of your choice*<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:smaller\"><em>*Must choose event and tickets when purchasing membership</em></span><br />\r\n<strong>$1,000 APPLAUSE LEVEL 1&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-size:smaller\"><em>(<u>$215 goes toward operations and is tax-deductible</u>)</em></span><br />\r\n1) Concert level benefits<br />\r\n2) One card for five free popcorns<br />\r\n3) One Fox Film Series movie pass good for 10 movie admissions ($45 value)<br />\r\n4) Two Season Tickets in Section A ($740 value)<br />\r\n<strong>$1,500 APPLAUSE LEVEL</strong><strong>&nbsp;2</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:smaller\">(<u>$715 goes toward operations and is tax-deductible</u>)</span><br />\r\n1) Concert level benefits<br />\r\n2) One card for five free popcorns<br />\r\n3) One Fox Film Series movie pass good for 10 movie admissions ($45 value)<br />\r\n4) Two Season Tickets in Section A ($740 value)<br />\r\n<strong>$2,000 APPLAUSE LEVEL 3</strong> <span style=\"font-size:smaller\">(<u>$1,215 goes toward operations and is tax-deductible</u>)</span><br />\r\n1) Concert level benefits<br />\r\n2) One card for five free popcorns<br />\r\n3) One Fox Film Series movie pass good for 10 movie admissions ($45 value)<br />\r\n4) Two Season Tickets in Section A ($740 value)<br />\r\n<strong>$2,500 OVATION LEVEL&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-size:smaller\"><em>(<u>$975 goes toward operations and is tax-deductible</u>)</em></span><br />\r\n1) Concert level benefits<br />\r\n2) One card for five free popcorns<br />\r\n3) One Fox Film Series movie pass good for 10 movie admissions ($45 value)<br />\r\n4) Four Season Tickets in Section A ($1,480 value)<br />\r\n<strong>$5,000 <span style=\"font-size:smaller\">(or more)</span> ENCORE LEVEL&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-size:smaller\"><em>(<u>$2,735 goes toward operations and is tax-deductible</u>)</em></span><br />\r\n1) Concert level benefits<br />\r\n2) One card for five free popcorns<br />\r\n3) One Fox Film Series movie pass good for 10 movie admissions ($45 value)<br />\r\n4) Six Season Tickets in Section A ($2,220 value)<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:x-large\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\"><strong>PLUS Level Memberships</strong></span></span><br />\r\n<em><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">What is a PLUS Level Membership? It&rsquo;s the same benefits for each membership level as listed above, but doesn&rsquo;t include tickets or a movie pass.<br />\r\nThis means when you select a PLUS Level Membership, <u>a full 100% of your membership dollars go directly toward helping the Fox with day-to-day expenses</u> (a PLUS for the Fox), <u>and then a full 100% of your Membership&nbsp;becomes TAX-DEDUCTIBLE</u>&nbsp;(a PLUS for you)!<br />\r\nYou can then purchase your tickets and movie passes separately.<br />\r\nPLUS Memberships are available for the $250 Curtain Raiser Membership and above.<br />\r\nInterested? It&rsquo;s easy! When you place your Membership order just say you want a PLUS Level Membership, and are declining your tickets and movie pass. Then purchase those separately. </span></em><br />\r\nThank you for supporting the Fox!<br />\r\nFor more information about Memberships, please contact Josh Davies at 620-663-5861 x 204.&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Memberships', 'support', 'memberships', 'memberships.php', 1, 0),
