(15, 'The Historic Hutchinson Fox Theatre - Hutchinson, Kansas', '<p><strong>Additional Support</strong><br />\r\n<strong>&quot;By the Bus&quot;</strong> If you would like to ignite a child&#39;s interest and participation in the arts, contact the Fox or mark your tax-deductible contribution &quot;By the Bus&quot;. By the Bus is the educational program offered by the Fox for children from area school districts and provides an opportunity for students to experience live theatre at no charge to them. This program is funded with foundation money, grants, and your contributions.<br />\r\n<strong>Building Prese</strong><strong>rvation Fund</strong> The Fox has a fund to maintain and preserve this beautiful facility. The Building Preservation Fund helps defray costs incurred in the preservation and maintenance of the building. $1.00 of each Fox ticket and a portion of rental tickets goes into this fund. Your contributions help with the rest. Any amount is appreciated, is tax-deductible, and may be added to your ticket order. The entire amount of your contribution will go to the preservation of this historic landmark.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Additional support', 'support', 'additional_support', 'additional_support.php', 1, 0);
